OL,5, An ex-BBC employee has said they raised
OL,6, concerns about "bullying" by Tim       
OL,7, Westwood when he was a Radio 1 DJ, but 
OL,8, "felt they were warned against taking  
OL,9, further action", the Guardian reported.
OL,11,FAnother former employee told the       
OL,12,Fnewspaper about a "sexist 'boys' club' 
OL,13,Fculture at Radio 1" during Westwood's  
OL,14,F19 years as a presenter.               
OL,16,FThe BBC has been asked for comment.    
OL,18,FEarlier this month the BBC revealed a  
OL,19,Fcomplaint against the DJ had previously
OL,20,Fbeen referred to police.               
